<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>Conical gradients interpolate colors counter-clockwise around a center point in Shape items.</db:para>
<db:note>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-shapes-shapegradient.xml#spread-prop">spread mode</db:link> setting has no effect for conical gradients.</db:para>
</db:note>
<db:note>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-shapes-conicalgradient.xml">ConicalGradient</db:link> is only supported in combination with Shape items. It is not compatible with <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-rectangle.xml">Rectangle</db:link>, as that only supports <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-gradient.xml">Gradient</db:link>.</db:para>
</db:note>
